The paper discusses the impact of pre-processing noise filtering on adversarial machine learning, which is a topic related to deep neural networks and their security. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
